attributes.long-description:
Lucky Start Bundle includes:
* 10 000 CREDITS
* 10 BAITCOINS
* 7-DAY PREMIUM
* 5 Marker Buoys
* 3 Small Storage Boxes (30 Slots)
* 2 Tackle Setups

Rods:
* ValueCast 200 SE
* OmniFloat 450 SE
Reels:
* LowDex 1500 P SE
* InspireCast 3000 SE

Lines:
* Braid .0055' (0.13 mm)
* Fluoro .008' (0.2 mm)
Spoons:
* Casting Spoon 1/4 Oz. (7 g) , 1/0 (x2)
* Narrow Spoon 1/4 Oz. (7 g), 1/0 (x2)
Bass Jigs:
* Mini Bass Jig 1/3 Oz. (9 g), 1
* Mini Bass Jig 1/3 Oz. (9 g), 2
Floats:
* Chubby (X2)
Hooks:
* Hook 2
* Hook 1
* Hook 1/0
Baits:

* Small Cutbait
* Small Minnows
* Grasshoppers
* Mayflies.

* Triple Case Rod Case
* MagFin™ EasyFish Lure Box
* FishHut S Plus Keepnet

LICENSES (7 days)

* Advanced Missouri License
